#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Entries"
msgstr "Vsebina menijev"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "This starts a new document in a new and independent editor window."
msgstr "S tem se začne nov dokument v novem in neodvisnem oknu urejevalnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create another window containing the current document. All changes to the "
"document in one window are reflected in the other window and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite drugo okno s trenutnim dokumentom. Vse spremembe dokumenta v enem "
"oknu se odražajo v drugem oknu in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a standard &kde; <guilabel>Open File</guilabel> dialog. Use the "
"file view to select the file you want to open, and click on <guibutton>Open</"
"guibutton> to open it."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže standardni &kde; Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Odpri datoteko</guilabel>. "
"Uporabite pogled datoteke, da izberete datoteko, ki jo želite odpreti, in "
"kliknite <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>, da jo odprete."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri nedavno</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a shortcut to open recently saved documents. Clicking on this item "
"opens a list to the side of the menu with several of the most recently saved "
"files. Clicking on a specific file will open it in &kappname; - if the file "
"still resides at the same location."
msgstr ""
"To je bližnjica za odpiranje nedavno shranjenih dokumentov. S klikom na ta "
"element se ob strani menija odpre seznam z več nazadnje shranjenimi "
"datotekami. S klikom na določeno datoteko se ta odpre v &kappname; - če je "
"datoteka še vedno na istem mestu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This saves the current document. If there has already been a save of the "
"document then this will overwrite the previously saved file without asking "
"for the user's consent. If it is the first save of a new document the save "
"as dialog (described below) will be invoked."
msgstr ""
"To shrani trenutni dokument. To shrani trenuten dokument. Če je dokument že "
"bil shranjen, bo prej shranjena datoteka prepisana, ne da bi bil uporabnik o "
"tem vprašan. Če gre za prvo shranjevanje novega dokumenta, bo poklicano "
"pogovorno okno 'Shrani kot' (opisano spodaj)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot ..."
"</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows a document to be saved with a new file name. This is done by "
"means of the file dialog box described above in the <link linkend=\"file-open"
"\">Open</link> section of this help file."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča shranjevanje dokumenta z novim imenom datoteke. To storite s "
"pomočjo pogovornega okna datoteke, opisanega zgoraj v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"file-open\">Odpri</link> te datoteke pomoči."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As with Encoding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot s kodiranjem</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save a document with a new file name in a different encoding."
msgstr "Shranite dokument z novim imenom datoteke v drugem kodiranju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Copy As</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kopijo kot</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save a copy of the document with a new file name and continue editing the "
"original document."
msgstr ""
"Shranite kopijo dokumenta z novim imenom datoteke in nadaljujte z urejanjem "
"izvirnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reloads the active file from disk. This command is useful if another program "
"or process has changed the file while you have it open in &kappname;."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži aktivno datoteko z diska. Ta ukaz je uporaben, če je drug "
"program ali proces spremenil datoteko, medtem ko jo imate odprto v "
"&kappname;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a simple print dialog allowing the user to specify what, where, and "
"how to print."
msgstr ""
"Odpre preprosto pogovorno okno za tiskanje, ki uporabniku omogoča, da "
"določi, kaj, kje in kako naj tiska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export as HTML</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi kot HTML</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the currently open document as an &HTML; file, which will be formatted "
"using the current syntax highlighting and color scheme settings."
msgstr ""
"Shranite trenutno odprt dokument kot &HTML; datoteka, ki bo oblikovana s "
"trenutnim označevanjem sintakse in nastavitvami barvne sheme."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the active file with this command. If you have made unsaved changes, "
"you will be prompted to save the file before &kappname; closes it."
msgstr ""
"S tem ukazom zaprite aktivno datoteko. Če ste naredili neshranjene "
"spremembe, boste pozvani, da shranite datoteko pred &kappname; ga zapre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will close the editor window, if you have more than one instance of "
"&kappname; running, through the <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem> menu items, those instances will not "
"be closed."
msgstr ""
"To bo zaprlo okno urejevalnika, če imate več kot en primerek &kappname; teče "
"prek elementov menija <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Novo "
"okno</guimenuitem>, ti primerki ne bodo zaprti."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last editing command (typing, copying, cutting &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Razveljavi zadnji ukaz za urejanje (tipkanje, kopiranje, rezanje &itd;)"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may undo several editing commands of the same type, like typing in "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"To lahko razveljavi več ukazov za urejanje iste vrste, na primer vnašanje "
"znakov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will reverse the most recent change (if any) made using Undo."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste razveljavili najnovejšo spremembo (če obstaja), narejeno s "
"funkcijo Razveljavi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the current selection and places it on the clipboard. "
"The clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to transfer data between "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz izbriše trenutni izbor in ga postavi v odložišče. Odložišče deluje "
"nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This copies the currently selected text to the clipboard so that it may be "
"pasted elsewhere. The clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to "
"transfer data between applications."
msgstr ""
"S tem kopirate trenutno izbrano besedilo v odložišče, da ga lahko prilepite "
"drugam. Odložišče deluje nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy as HTML</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj kot HTML</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selection as &HTML;, formatted using the current syntax "
"highlighting and color scheme settings."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte izbor kot &HTML;, oblikovan z uporabo trenutnega označevanja "
"sintakse in nastavitev barvne sheme."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will insert the first item in the clipboard at the cursor position. The "
"clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to transfer data between "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"To bo vstavilo prvi element v odložišče na položaj kazalke. Odložišče deluje "
"nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Overwrite Selection is enabled, the pasted text will overwrite the "
"selection, if any."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost Prepiši izbor, bo prilepljeno besedilo prepisalo "
"izbor, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Ins;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Ins;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi izbor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will paste the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">mouse selection</ulink> contents "
"that were chosen previously. Mark some text with the mouse pointer to paste "
"it in the currently open file using this menu item."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste prilepili vsebino <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">izbire miške</ulink>, ki je bila "
"predhodno izbrana. Označite nekaj besedila s kazalcem miške, da ga prilepite "
"v trenutno odprto datoteko s tem elementom menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Swap with clipboard contents</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zamenjaj z vsebino odložišča</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will swap the selected text with the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">clipboard</ulink> contents."
msgstr ""
"To bo zamenjalo izbrano besedilo z vsebino <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">odložišča</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clipboard History Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi zgodovino odložišča</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open a dialog to select and paste an entry from the clipboard "
"history."
msgstr ""
"To bo odprlo pogovorno okno za izbiro in lepljenje vnosa iz zgodovine "
"odložišča."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Input Modes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Načini vnosa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch between a normal and a vi-like, modal editing mode. The vi input mode "
"supports the most used commands and motions from vim's normal and visual "
"mode and has an optional vi mode statusbar. This status bar shows commands "
"while they are being entered, output from commands and the current mode. The "
"behavior of this mode can be configured in the <link linkend=\"pref-edit-vi-"
"input-mode\">Vi Input Mode</link> tab of the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> "
"page in &kappname;'s settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljajte med običajnim in modalnim načinom urejanja, podobnim vi. Način "
"vnosa vi podpira najpogosteje uporabljene ukaze in gibe iz normalnega in "
"vizualnega načina vim in ima izbirno statusno vrstico načina vi. Ta statusna "
"vrstica prikazuje ukaze med vnašanjem, izhod iz ukazov in trenutni način. "
"Delovanje tega načina je mogoče konfigurirati na zavihku <link linkend="
"\"pref-edit-vi-input-mode\">Način vnosa Vi</link> na strani "
"<guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> v &kappname; pogovorno okno z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ins;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Overwrite Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ins;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način prepisovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the Insert/Overwrite modes. When the mode is <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, you insert characters where the cursor is. When the mode is "
"<guilabel>OVR</guilabel>, writing characters will replace the current "
"characters if your cursor is positioned before any character. The status bar "
"shows the current state of the Overwrite Mode, either <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>OVR</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi med načini Vstavljanje/Prepisovanje. Ko je način <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, vstavite znake tam, kjer je kazalka. Ko je način <guilabel>OVR</"
"guilabel>, bodo pisni znaki zamenjali trenutne znake, če je vaša kazalka "
"postavljena pred kateri koli znak. Statusna vrstica prikazuje trenutno "
"stanje načina prepisovanja, <guilabel>INS</guilabel> ali <guilabel>OVR</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Read Only Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način samo za branje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current document to Read Only mode. This prevents any text addition "
"and any changes in the document formatting."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite trenutni dokument v način samo za branje. To prepreči kakršno koli "
"dodajanje besedila in kakršne koli spremembe v oblikovanju dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the incremental search bar at the bottom of the editor window. On "
"the left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed "
"by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za postopno iskanje na dnu okna urejevalnika. Na levi "
"strani vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno "
"besedilno polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start entering characters of your search pattern, the search starts "
"immediately. If there is a match in the text this is highlighted and the "
"background color of the entry field changes to light green. If the search "
"pattern does not match any string in the text, this is indicated by a light "
"red background color of the entry field."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete vnašati znake svojega iskalnega vzorca, se iskanje začne takoj. "
"Če se besedilo ujema, je to označeno in barva ozadja vnosnega polja se "
"spremeni v svetlo zeleno. Če se iskalni vzorec ne ujema z nobenim nizom v "
"besedilu, je to označeno s svetlo rdečo barvo ozadja vnosnega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:388 menus.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> or "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to jump to the "
"next or previous match in the document."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> gumb za skok na "
"naslednje ali prejšnje ujemanje v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches in the document are highlighted even when you close the search bar. "
"To clear this highlighting, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr ""
"Ujemanja v dokumentu so označena tudi, ko zaprete iskalno vrstico. Če želite "
"počistiti to označevanje, pritisnite &Esc; ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the search should be case sensitive. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali naj iskanje razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. Če "
"izberete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili najdbe na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the incremental search bar to switch to the power "
"search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Klikni na gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configure-shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> za preklop med vrsticami za iskanje in zamenjavo moči."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Poišči naslednje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar, and searching forwards through the document starting "
"from the cursor position."
msgstr ""
"S tem se ponovi zadnja operacija iskanja, če obstaja, brez priklica vrstice "
"za inkrementalno iskanje in iskanja naprej po dokumentu, začenši od položaja "
"kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar, and searching backwards instead of forwards through "
"the document."
msgstr ""
"S tem se ponovi zadnja operacija iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica prirastne "
"iskalne vrstice in iskanja nazaj namesto naprej po dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Selected</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Poišči Izbrano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds next occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče naslednjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Find Selected Backwards</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Poišči izbrano za nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds previous occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče prejšnjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Replace...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zamenjaj ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command opens the power search and replace bar. On the upper left side "
"of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed by a small "
"text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz odpre vrstico za iskanje in zamenjavo. Na zgornji levi strani "
"vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno besedilno "
"polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the search mode by selecting <guilabel>Plain text</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Whole words</guilabel>, <guilabel>Escape sequences</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</guilabel> from the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Način iskanja lahko nadzirate tako, da na padajočem meniju izberete "
"<guilabel>Navadno besedilo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Cele besede</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni izraz</"
"guilabel> navzdol škatla."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Escape sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</"
"guilabel> are selected, the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> menuitem at the "
"bottom of the context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you "
"to add escape sequences or regular expression items to the search or replace "
"pattern from predefined lists."
msgstr ""
"Če so izbrana <guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni "
"izraz</guilabel>, bo omogočen menijski element <guibutton>Dodaj ...</"
"guibutton> na dnu priročnega menija besedilnih polj in vam omogoča dodajanje "
"ubežnih zaporedij ali postavk regularnega izraza v vzorec iskanja ali "
"zamenjave iz vnaprej določenih seznamov."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the text to replace with in the text box labeled <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> and click the <guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace "
"only the highlighted text or the <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> button "
"to replace the search text in the whole document."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje z oznako <guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel> vnesite besedilo, s "
"katerim želite zamenjati, in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, "
"da zamenjate samo označeno besedilo, ali gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj vse</"
"guibutton>, da zamenjajte iskalno besedilo v celotnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the search and replace behavior by selecting different "
"options at the bottom of the bar. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern. <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> will search and replace within the current selection "
"only. The <guilabel>Find All</guilabel> button highlights all matches in the "
"document and shows the number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Obnašanje iskanja in zamenjave lahko spremenite tako, da izberete različne "
"možnosti na dnu vrstice. Če izberete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili najdbe na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu. "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> bo iskal in zamenjal "
"samo znotraj trenutnega izbora. Gumb <guilabel>Najdi vse</guilabel> označi "
"vse zadetke v dokumentu in prikaže število najdenih zadetkov v majhnem "
"pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the power search and replace bar to switch to the "
"incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> na "
"desni strani zmogljive vrstice za iskanje in zamenjavo za preklopite na "
"vrstico za postopno iskanje."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Selection Menu"
msgstr "Izbirni meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will select the entire document. This could be very useful for copying "
"the entire file to another application."
msgstr ""
"To bo izbralo celoten dokument. To je lahko zelo uporabno za prepisovanje "
"celotne datoteke v drug program."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prekliči "
"izbiro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deselects the selected text in the editor if any."
msgstr "Prekliče izbiro izbranega besedila v urejevalniku, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Block "
"Selection Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Blokiraj način "
"izbire</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles Selection Mode. When the Selection Mode is <guilabel>BLOCK</"
"guilabel>, the status bar contains the string <guilabel>[BLOCK]</guilabel> "
"and you can make vertical selections, &eg; select column 5 to 10 in lines 9 "
"to 15."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi način izbire. Ko je izbirni način <guilabel>BLOKIRAJ</guilabel>, "
"statusna vrstica vsebuje niz <guilabel>[BLOKIRAJ]</guilabel> in lahko "
"izbirate navpično, &eg; izberite stolpec od 5 do 10 v vrsticah od 9 do 15."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbor</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This adds one space to the beginning of the line where the text cursor is "
"located or to the beginning of any selected lines."
msgstr ""
"To doda presledek na začetek vrstice, kjer se nahaja kurzor ali pa na "
"pričetek vsake izbrane vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uncomment</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odkomentiraj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This removes one space (if any exist) from the beginning of the line where "
"the text cursor is located or from the beginning of any selected lines."
msgstr ""
"To odstrani presledek (če obstaja) z začetka vrstice, kjer se nahaja kurzor "
"ali z začetka vsake izbrane vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Join Lines</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Združi vrstice</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the selected lines, or the current line and the line below with one "
"white space character as a separator. Leading/trailing white space on joined "
"lines is removed in the affected ends."
msgstr ""
"Združi izbrane vrstice ali trenutno vrstico in spodnjo vrstico z enim "
"presledkom kot ločilom. Začetni/zadnji prazen prostor na spojenih črtah je "
"odstranjen na prizadetih koncih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Capitalization</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pisanje velikih "
"začetnic</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capitalize the selected text or the current word."
msgstr "Napiši izbrano besedilo ali trenutno besedo z veliko začetnico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uppercase</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Velike črke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the selected text or the letter after the cursor in uppercase."
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo ali črko za kazalko postavite v velike črke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lowercase</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Male črke</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the selected text or the letter after the cursor in lowercase."
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo ali črko za kazalko vstavite z malimi črkami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clean Indentation</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Čisti zamik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This cleans the indentation for the current selection or for the line the "
"cursor is currently in. Cleaning the indentation ensures that all your "
"selected text follows the indentation mode you choose."
msgstr ""
"To počisti zamik za trenutni izbor ali za vrstico, v kateri je trenutno "
"kazalec. Čiščenje zamika zagotovi, da vse vaše izbrano besedilo sledi načinu "
"zamika, ki ga izberete."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Format Indent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Izbor</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Oblika zamika</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes a realign of the current line or selected lines using the indentation "
"mode and indentation settings in the document."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči ponovno poravnavo trenutne vrstice ali izbranih vrstic z uporabo "
"načina zamika in nastavitev zamika v dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Align On...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poravnaj na ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command aligns lines in the selected block or whole document on the "
"column given by a regular expression that you will be prompted for."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz poravna vrstice v izbranem bloku ali celotnem dokumentu na stolpec, "
"ki ga poda regularni izraz, za katerega boste pozvani."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you give an empty pattern it will align on the first non-blank character "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Če podate prazen vzorec, se bo privzeto poravnal s prvim znakom, ki ni "
"prazen."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the pattern has a capture it will indent on the captured match."
msgstr "Če ima vzorec zajem, se bo zajeto ujemanje zamaknilo."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: menus.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With '<userinput>-</userinput>' it will insert spaces before the first '-' "
"of each lines to align them all on the same column."
msgstr ""
"Z '<userinput>-</userinput>' bo vstavil presledke pred prvi '-' vsake "
"vrstice, da jih vse poravna v isti stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With '<userinput>alignon :\\\\s+(.)</userinput>' it will insert spaces "
"before the first non-blank character that occurs after a colon to align them "
"all on the same column."
msgstr ""
"Z '<userinput>alignon :\\\\s (.)</userinput>' bo vstavil presledke pred prvi "
"neprazen znak, ki se pojavi za dvopičjem, da jih vse poravna v isti stolpec."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izbor</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi prelom besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apply static word wrapping on all the document. That means that a new line "
"of text will automatically start when the current line exceeds the length "
"specified by the <guilabel>Wrap words at</guilabel> option in the Editing "
"tab in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite statično prelivanje besed na celotnem dokumentu. To pomeni, da se "
"bo nova vrstica besedila samodejno začela, ko trenutna vrstica preseže "
"dolžino, določeno z možnostjo <guilabel>Prelomi besede v</guilabel> na "
"zavihku Urejanje v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem "
">Meni Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Caret above Cursor</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj kazalko nad kazalko</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds another caret above the current cursor. The caret is placed in the line "
"directly above and in the same column as the current cursor."
msgstr ""
"Doda drugo kazalko nad trenutno kazalko. Kazalka je postavljena v vrstico "
"neposredno nad in v isti stolpec kot trenutna kazalka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Caret below Cursor</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj kazalko pod kazalko</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds another caret below the current cursor. The caret is placed in the line "
"directly above and in the same column as the current cursor."
msgstr ""
"Doda drugo kazalko pod trenutno kazalko. Kazalka je postavljena v vrstico "
"neposredno nad in v isti stolpec kot trenutna kazalka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Cursors "
"to Line Ends</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj kazalke "
"na konce vrstice</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds a cursor to every currently selected line."
msgstr "Doda kazalko v vsako trenutno izbrano vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find and Select Next "
"Occurrence</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči in izberi naslednjo "
"pojavitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finds the next occurrence of the word currently under the cursor, selects it "
"and adds a cursor."
msgstr ""
"Poišče naslednjo pojavitev besede, ki je trenutno pod kazalko, jo izbere in "
"doda kazalko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find and "
"Select All Occurrences</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči in "
"izberi vse pojavitve</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finds all occurrences of the word currently under the cursor, selects them "
"and adds a cursor for each of them."
msgstr ""
"Poišče vse pojavitve besede, ki je trenutno pod kazalko, jih izbere in za "
"vsako od njih doda kazalko."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enlarge Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid "This increases the display font size."
msgstr "To poveča velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrink Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skrči pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid "This decreases the display font size."
msgstr "To zmanjša velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dynamic Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelom Besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dinamični Prelom Besed </guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles dynamic word wrap in the current view. Dynamic word wrap makes all "
"the text in a view visible without the need for horizontal scrolling by "
"rendering one actual line on more visual lines as needed."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi dinamični prelom besed v trenutnem pogledu. Dinamično prelivanje "
"besed omogoča, da je celotno besedilo v pogledu vidno brez potrebe po "
"vodoravnem pomikanju, tako da po potrebi upodablja eno dejansko vrstico v "
"več vizualnih vrsticah."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Dynamic Word Wrap Indicators</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelom besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Kazalniki dinamičnega preloma besed</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when and how the dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed. "
"This is only available if the <guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> option "
"is checked."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kdaj in kako naj bodo prikazani indikatorji dinamičnega preloma "
"besed. To je na voljo le, če je označena možnost <guilabel>Dinamični prelom "
"besed</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Static Word Wrap Marker</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelivanje besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži oznako statičnega prelivanja besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a vertical line will be drawn at the word wrap "
"column as defined in the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the Editing "
"tab. Please note that the word wrap marker is only drawn if you use a fixed "
"pitch font."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo na stolpcu za prelom besed narisana navpična "
"črta, kot je definirano v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"Zavihek za urejanje. Upoštevajte, da je oznaka za prelom besed narisana le, "
"če uporabljate pisavo s fiksno višino."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži obrobo ikone</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle item. Setting it on checked will make the Icon Border "
"visible in the left side of the active editor, and vice versa. The Icon "
"Border indicates the positions of the marked lines in the editor."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če je označeno, bo obroba ikone vidna na levi "
"strani aktivnega urejevalnika in obratno. Obroba ikone označuje položaje "
"označenih vrstic v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži številke vrstic</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle Item. Setting it on checked will make a pane displaying the "
"line numbers of the document visible in the left border of the active "
"editor, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če ga nastavite na označeno, bo podokno, ki "
"prikazuje številke vrstic dokumenta, vidno na levem robu aktivnega "
"urejevalnika in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Marks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži "
"oznake drsnega traku</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the view will show marks on the vertical "
"scrollbar. The marks are equivalent to the marks on the <link linkend=\"view-"
"show-icon-border\">Icon Border</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo v pogledu prikazane oznake na navpičnem "
"drsnem traku. Oznake so enakovredne oznakam na <link linkend=\"view-show-"
"icon-border\">obrobi ikone</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Mini-Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"mini zemljevid z drsnim trakom</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will replace the scrollbar with a visualization of the current "
"document. For more information on the scrollbar minimap, see <xref linkend="
"\"kate-part-scrollbar-minimap\"/>."
msgstr ""
"To bo zamenjalo drsni trak z vizualizacijo trenutnega dokumenta. Za več "
"informacij o mini zemljevidu z drsnim trakom glejte <xref linkend=\"kate-"
"part-scrollbar-minimap\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Code Folding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zgibanje kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options pertain to <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">code folding</ulink>:"
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti se nanašajo na <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-"
"tools-code-folding.html\">zlaganje kode</ulink>:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Code "
"Folding</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Zgibanje "
"kode</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži zgibne oznake</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the folding marker pane in the left side of the view."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz zložljivega podokna označevalcev na levi strani pogleda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Code Folding</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Fold Current Node</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zlaganje kode</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zlaganje trenutnega vozlišča</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Strni območje, ki vsebuje kazalko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Code Folding</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unfold Current Node</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zgibanje kode</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razgrni trenutno vozlišče</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Razširite območje, ki vsebuje kazalec."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Code Folding</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Fold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zlaganje kode</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Zloži vozlišča najvišje ravni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collapse all toplevel regions in the document. Click on the right pointing "
"triangle to expand all toplevel regions."
msgstr ""
"Strni vse regije najvišje ravni v dokumentu. Kliknite desni trikotnik, da "
"razširite vse regije najvišje ravni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Code Folding</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Unfold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zlaganje kode</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Razgrni vozlišča najvišje ravni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand all toplevel regions in the document."
msgstr "Razširite vse regije najvišje ravni v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Non-Printable Spaces"
msgstr "Pokaži nenatisljive prostore"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/hide bounding box around non-printable spaces."
msgstr "Pokaži/skrij omejevalni okvir okoli nenatisljivih presledkov."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Go Menu"
msgstr "Pojdi meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Line...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na vrstico ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the goto line bar at the bottom of the window which is used to "
"have the cursor jump to a particular line (specified by number) in the "
"document. The line number may be entered directly into the text box or "
"graphically by clicking on the up or down arrow spin controls at the side of "
"the text box. The little up arrow will increase the line number and the down "
"arrow decrease it. Close the bar with a click on the button with an icon on "
"the left side of the bar."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za prehod na vrstico na dnu okna, ki se uporablja za skok "
"kazalca na določeno vrstico (določeno s številko) v dokumentu. Številko "
"vrstice lahko vnesete neposredno v besedilno polje ali grafično s klikom na "
"puščico gor ali dol ob strani besedilnega polja. Majhna puščica navzgor "
"poveča številko vrstice, puščica navzdol pa zmanjša. Vrstico zapremo s "
"klikom na gumb z ikono na levi strani vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Previous Editing Line</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na prejšnjo vrstico za "
"urejanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action jumps the previous editing line in the <link linkend="
"\"multicursor-modifier-configure\">multicursor configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje preskoči prejšnjo vrstico za urejanje v <link linkend="
"\"multicursor-modifier-configure\">konfiguraciji več kazalk</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Next Editing "
"Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na "
"naslednjo vrstico za urejanje</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action jumps the next editing line in the <link linkend=\"multicursor-"
"modifier-configure\">multicursor configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje preskoči na naslednjo vrstico za urejanje v <link linkend="
"\"multicursor-modifier-configure\">konfiguracija več kazalk</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Previous Modified Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na prejšnjo spremenjeno vrstico</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that were changed since opening the file are called modified lines. "
"This action jumps the previous modified line."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki so bile spremenjene od odprtja datoteke, se imenujejo "
"spremenjene vrstice. To dejanje preskoči prejšnjo spremenjeno vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Next Modified Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na naslednjo spremenjeno "
"vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that were changed since opening the file are called modified lines. "
"This action jumps the next modified line."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki so bile spremenjene od odprtja datoteke, se imenujejo "
"spremenjene vrstice. To dejanje preskoči naslednjo spremenjeno vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Matching Bracket</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na ujemajoči oklepaj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the cursor to the associated opening or closing bracket."
msgstr "Kazalko premaknite na ustrezni začetni ali zaključni oklepaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select to Matching "
"Bracket</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi ujemajoči "
"se oklepaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the text between associated opening and closing brackets."
msgstr "Izbere besedilo med povezanimi začetnimi in končnimi oklepaji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bookmarks</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zaznamki</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the entries described here, one entry for each bookmark in the active "
"document will be available. The text will be the first few words of the "
"marked line. Choose an item to move the cursor to the start of that line. "
"The editor will scroll as necessary to make that line visible."
msgstr ""
"Pod tukaj opisanimi vnosi bo na voljo en vnos za vsak zaznamek v aktivnem "
"dokumentu. Besedilo bo prvih nekaj besed označene vrstice. Izberite element, "
"da premaknete kazalec na začetek te vrstice. Urejevalnik se bo po potrebi "
"pomaknil, da bo ta vrstica vidna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bookmarks</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zaznamki</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nastavi zaznamek </guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets or removes a bookmark in the current line of the active document. (If "
"it's there, it is removed, otherwise one is set.)"
msgstr ""
"Nastavi ali odstrani zaznamek v trenutni vrstici aktivnega dokumenta. (Če je "
"tam, je odstranjen, drugače je nastavljen.)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bookmarks</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Clear "
"All Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zaznamki</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Počisti vse zaznamke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will remove all the markers from the document as well as the "
"list of markers which is appended at the bottom of this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo odstranil vse označevalce iz dokumenta in tudi seznam "
"označevalcev, ki je pripet na dnu tega elementa menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bookmarks</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zaznamki</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the first above line with a "
"bookmark. The menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece "
"of text on the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in "
"a line above the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalec premakne na začetek prve zgornje vrstice z zaznamkom. "
"Besedilo menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del "
"besedila v vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici nad kazalcem "
"zaznamek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Bookmarks</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Next</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zaznamki</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the next line with a bookmark. The "
"menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece of text on "
"the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in a line "
"below the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalec premakne na začetek naslednje vrstice z zaznamkom. Besedilo "
"menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del besedila v "
"vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici pod kazalcem zaznamek."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mode</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the filetype scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global filetype mode set in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"Filetypes tab for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo vrste datoteke, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To "
"prepiše globalni način vrste datoteke, nastavljen v <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> na zavihku Vrste datotek samo za vaš trenutni "
"dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poudarjanje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the Highlighting scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global highlighting mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo označevanja, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način označevanja, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Indentation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zamik</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the style of indentation you want for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global indentation mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite slog zamika, ki ga želite za svoj aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način zamika, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kodiranje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can overwrite the default encoding set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Open/Save</guilabel> page to set a different "
"encoding for your current document. The encoding you set here will be only "
"valid for your current document."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto kodiranje lahko prepišete v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> na strani <guilabel>Odpri/Shrani</guilabel>, da nastavite "
"drugačno kodiranje za vaš trenutni dokument. Kodiranje, ki ga nastavite "
"tukaj, bo veljavno samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Add Byte Mark Order (BOM)</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dodaj vrstni red oznak bajtov (BOM)</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this action you can explicitly add a byte order mark for unicode "
"encoded documents. The byte order mark (BOM) is a Unicode character used to "
"signal the endianness (byte order) of a text file or stream, for more "
"information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark"
"\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to dejanje, lahko izrecno dodate oznako vrstnega reda bajtov za "
"dokumente, kodirane z Unicode. Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov (BOM) je znak "
"Unicode, ki se uporablja za signalizacijo endianness (vrstni red bajtov) "
"besedilne datoteke ali toka, za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\" >Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>End of Line</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Konec vrstice</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global end of line mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite želeni način konca vrstice za vaš aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način konca vrstice, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu contains a list of all scripted actions. The list can easily be "
"modified by <link linkend=\"dev-scripting-command-line\">writing your own "
"scripts</link>. This way, &katepart; can be extended with user-defined tools."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni vsebuje seznam vseh skriptiranih dejanj. Seznam lahko preprosto "
"spremenite tako, da <link linkend=\"dev-scripting-command-line\">napišete "
"lastne skripte</link>. Na ta način &katepart; se lahko razširi z uporabniško "
"določenimi orodji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigacija</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Up;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigation</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move cursor to previous "
"matching indent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Up;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigacija</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni kazalec na "
"prejšnji ujemajoči se zamik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the cursor to the first line above the current line that is indented "
"at the same level as the current line."
msgstr ""
"Premakne kazalec v prvo vrstico nad trenutno vrstico, ki je zamaknjena na "
"isti ravni kot trenutna vrstica."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigation</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move cursor to next "
"matching indent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Navigacija</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni kazalec na "
"naslednji ujemajoči se zamik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the cursor to the first line below the current line that is indented "
"at the same level as the current line."
msgstr ""
"Premakne kazalko v prvo vrstico pod trenutno vrstico, ki je zamaknjena na "
"isti ravni kot trenutna vrstica."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Sort Selected Text</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Razvrsti izbrano besedilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorts the selected text or whole document in ascending order."
msgstr ""
"Razvrsti izbrano besedilo ali celoten dokument v naraščajočem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move Lines Down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni vrstice navzdol</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected lines down."
msgstr "Premakni izbrane vrstice navzdol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Up;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move Lines Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Up;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni vrstice navzgor</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected lines up."
msgstr "Premakni izbrane vrstice navzgor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Duplicate Selected Lines Down</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Podvoji izbrane vrstice "
"navzdol</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicates the selected lines down."
msgstr "Podvoji izbrane vrstice navzdol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Duplicate Selected Lines Up</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Podvoji izbrane vrstice "
"navzgor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicates the selected lines up."
msgstr "Podvoji izbrane vrstice navzgor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>URI-encode selected text</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>URI kodiraj izbrano besedilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Encodes the selected text so that it can be used as part of a query string "
"in a &URL;, replacing the selection with the encoded text."
msgstr ""
"Kodira izbrano besedilo, tako da ga je mogoče uporabiti kot del "
"poizvedbenega niza v &URL;, pri čemer zamenja izbor s kodiranim besedilom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Editing</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>URI-decode selected text</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Urejanje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>URI-dekodiranje izbranega "
"besedila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If part of the query string of a &URL; is selected, this will decode it and "
"replace the selection with the original raw text."
msgstr ""
"Če je del poizvedbenega niza &URL; je izbran, ga bo to dekodiralo in "
"zamenjalo izbor z izvirnim neobdelanim besedilom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Expand abbreviation</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Razširi kratico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Converts the selected text to a pair of opening and closing &HTML; or &XML; "
"tags. For example, if <userinput>div</userinput> is selected, this item will "
"replace that with <computeroutput>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Pretvori izbrano besedilo v par odpiralnih in zapiralnih &HTML; ali &XML; "
"oznake. Če je na primer izbran <userinput>div</userinput>, bo ta element to "
"nadomestil z <computeroutput>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Wrap with tag</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prelomi z oznako</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wraps the selected text with the tag provided on the <link linkend=\"dev-"
"scripting-command-line\">command line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prelomi izbrano besedilo z oznako v <link linkend=\"dev-scripting-command-"
"line\">ukazni vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move cursor to matching tag</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni kazalko na ustrezno "
"oznako</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the cursor is inside an opening &HTML;/&XML; tag, this item will move it "
"to the closing tag. If the cursor is inside the closing tag, it will instead "
"move it to the opening tag."
msgstr ""
"Če je kazalec znotraj odprtine &HTML;/&XML; Ta element ga bo premaknil na "
"zaključno oznako. Če je kazalec znotraj končne oznake, ga bo premaknil na "
"začetno oznako."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select &HTML;/&XML; tag contents inwards</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izberite &HTML;/&XML; označi "
"vsebino navznoter</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the cursor is inside a pair of &HTML;/&XML; tags, this option will "
"change the selection to include the contents of those &HTML;/&XML; tags, "
"without selecting the tags themselves."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kazalec znotraj para &HTML;/&XML; oznak bo ta možnost spremenila "
"izbiro tako, da bo vključevala vsebino tistih &HTML;/&XML; oznake, ne da bi "
"same oznake izbrali."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select &HTML;/&XML; tag contents outwards</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izberite &HTML;/&XML; označi "
"vsebino navzven</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the cursor is inside a pair of &HTML;/&XML; tags, this item will change "
"the selection to include the contents of those &HTML;/&XML; tags, including "
"the tags themselves."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kazalec znotraj para &HTML;/&XML; oznak bo ta element spremenil izbor "
"tako, da bo vključeval vsebino tistih &HTML;/&XML; oznake, vključno s samimi "
"oznakami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Toggle Comment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Preklopi komentar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the selected portion is not a comment, this item will enclose that "
"portion in &HTML;/&XML; comments (&eg; <computeroutput>&lt;!-- selected text "
"--&gt;</computeroutput>). If the selected portion is a comment, the comment "
"tags will be removed instead."
msgstr ""
"Če izbrani del ni komentar, bo ta element ta del priložil v &HTML;/&XML; "
"komentarji (&eg; <computeroutput>&lt;!-- izbrano besedilo --&gt;</"
"computeroutput>). Če je izbrani del komentar, bodo namesto tega odstranjene "
"oznake komentarjev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Delete tag under cursor</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši oznako pod kazalcem</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the cursor is presently inside a &HTML;/&XML; tag, this item will delete "
"the entire tag."
msgstr ""
"Če je kazalec trenutno znotraj &HTML;/&XML; bo ta element izbrisal celotno "
"oznako."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Decrement number by 1</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Zmanjšaj število za 1</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will subtract one from the currently selected text, if it is a "
"number. For example, if <userinput>5</userinput> is selected, it will become "
"<computeroutput>4</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo od trenutno izbranega besedila odštel eno, če je številka. Če "
"je na primer izbran <userinput>5</userinput>, bo postal <computeroutput>4</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Decrement number by 10</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Zmanjšaj število za 10</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will subtract 10 from the currently selected text, if it is a "
"number. For example, if <userinput>15</userinput> is selected, it will "
"become <computeroutput>5</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo od trenutno izbranega besedila odštel 10, če je to število. Če "
"je na primer izbran <userinput>15</userinput>, bo postal <computeroutput>5</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Decrement number by 0.1</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Zmanjšaj število za 0,1</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will subtract 0.1 from the currently selected text, if it is a "
"number. For example, if <userinput>4.5</userinput> is selected, it will "
"become <computeroutput>4.4</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo od trenutno izbranega besedila odštel 0,1, če je to število. "
"Če je na primer izbran <userinput>4.5</userinput>, bo postal "
"<computeroutput>4.4</computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Increment number by 1</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj število za 1</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will add one to the currently selected text, if it is a number. "
"For example, if <userinput>5</userinput> is selected, it will become "
"<computeroutput>6</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo trenutno izbranemu besedilu dodal eno, če je številka. Če je "
"na primer izbran <userinput>5</userinput>, bo postal <computeroutput>6</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Increment number by 10</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj število za 10</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will add 10 to the currently selected text, if it is a number. For "
"example, if <userinput>5</userinput> is selected, it will become "
"<computeroutput>15</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo trenutno izbranemu besedilu dodal 10, če je to število. Če je "
"na primer izbran <userinput>5</userinput>, bo postal <computeroutput>15</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Emmet</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Increment number by 0.1</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Emmet</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj število za 0,1</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item will add 0.1 to the currently selected text, if it is a number. "
"For example, if <userinput>4.5</userinput> is selected, it will become "
"<computeroutput>4.6</computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element bo trenutno izbranemu besedilu dodal 0,1, če je to številka. Če "
"je na primer izbran <userinput>4.5</userinput>, bo postal "
"<computeroutput>4.6</computeroutput>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preklopi na ukazno vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the &katepart; command line at the bottom of the window. In the "
"command line, type <userinput>help</userinput> to get help and "
"<userinput>help list</userinput> to get a list of commands. For more "
"information on the command line, see <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-"
"commandline\">The Editor Component Command Line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže &katepart; ukazno vrstico na dnu okna. V ukazno vrstico vnesite "
"<userinput>pomoč</userinput>, da dobite pomoč, in <userinput>seznam pomoči</"
"userinput>, da dobite seznam ukazov. Za več informacij o ukazni vrstici "
"glejte <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">Ukazna vrstica "
"komponente urejevalnika</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invoke Code Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikliči dokončanje kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manually invoke command completion, usually by using a shortcut bound to "
"this action."
msgstr ""
"Ročno prikličite dokončanje ukaza, običajno z uporabo bližnjice, vezane na "
"to dejanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1658
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Word Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dokončanje besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Reuse Word Below</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) and <guimenuitem>Reuse Word Above</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo>) complete the currently typed text by searching for similar words "
"backward or forward from the current cursor position. <guimenuitem>Shell "
"Completion</guimenuitem> pops up a completion box with matching entries."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Znova uporabi besedo spodaj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) in <guimenuitem>Ponovno "
"uporabi besedo zgoraj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action= \"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>) dokončajte trenutno vneseno besedilo z "
"iskanjem podobnih besed nazaj ali naprej od trenutnega položaja kazalca. "
"<guimenuitem>Dokončanje lupine</guimenuitem> odpre polje za dokončanje z "
"ujemajočimi se vnosi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem> is enabled, wrongly "
"spelled text is underlined in the document on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno <guimenuitem>Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>, "
"je napačno črkovano besedilo v dokumentu sproti podčrtano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Črkovanje ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to "
"help the user catch and correct any spelling errors.</action> Clicking on "
"this entry will start the checker and bring up the speller dialog box "
"through which the user can control the process. There are four settings "
"lined up vertically in the center of the dialog with their corresponding "
"labels just to the left. Starting at the top they are:"
msgstr ""
"<action>S tem se zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja – program, ki je "
"zasnovan tako, da uporabniku pomaga odkriti in popraviti morebitne črkovalne "
"napake.</action> S klikom na ta vnos se bo zagnal preverjevalnik in "
"prikazalo se pogovorno okno črkovalnika, prek katerega lahko uporabnik "
"nadzira postopek . Na sredini pogovornega okna so navpično poravnane štiri "
"nastavitve z ustreznimi oznakami na levi strani. Začenši na vrhu so:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unknown word:"
msgstr "Neznana beseda:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, the spellchecker indicates the word currently under consideration. "
"This happens when the checker encounters a word not in its dictionary - a "
"file containing a list of correctly spelled words against which it compares "
"each word in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj črkovalnik označuje besedo, ki je trenutno v obravnavi. To se zgodi, "
"ko preverjevalnik naleti na besedo, ki je ni v njegovem slovarju - datoteko, "
"ki vsebuje seznam pravilno črkovanih besed, s katerimi primerja vsako besedo "
"v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace with:"
msgstr "Zamenjaj z:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the checker has any similar words in its dictionary the first one will be "
"listed here. The user can accept the suggestion, type in his or her own "
"correction, or choose a different suggestion from the next box."
msgstr ""
"Če ima preverjevalnik podobne besede v svojem slovarju, bo prva navedena "
"tukaj. Če črkovalnik najde v slovarju podobne besede, bo prva prikaza tukaj. "
"Uporabnik lahko izbere predlog, vtipka svoj lasten popravek ali pa izbere "
"drugačen predlog iz naslednjega polja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language:"
msgstr "Jezik:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed multiple dictionaries, here you can select which "
"dictionary/language should be used."
msgstr ""
"Če ste namestili več slovarjev, lahko tukaj izberete, kateri slovar/jezik "
"želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right side of the dialog box are 6 buttons that allow the user to "
"control the spellcheck process. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani pogovornega okna je 6 gumbov, ki uporabniku omogočajo nadzor "
"nad postopkom preverjanja črkovanja. To so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Dictionary"
msgstr "Dodaj v slovar"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing this button adds the <guilabel>Unknown word </guilabel> to the "
"checker's dictionary. This means that in the future the checker will always "
"consider this word to be correctly spelled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete ta gumb, dodate <guilabel>Neznano besedo </guilabel> v slovar "
"pregledovalnika. To pomeni, da bo pregledovalec v prihodnje to besedo vedno "
"štel za pravilno črkovano."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suggest"
msgstr "Predlagaj"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The checker may list here a number of possible replacements for the word "
"under consideration. Clicking on any one of the suggestions will cause that "
"word to be entered in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box, above."
msgstr ""
"Preverjevalec lahko tukaj navede številne možne zamenjave za obravnavano "
"besedo. Če kliknete katerega koli od predlogov, bo ta beseda vnesena v polje "
"<guilabel>Zamenjaj z</guilabel> zgoraj."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Zamenjaj"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button has the checker replace the word under consideration in the "
"document with the word in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"S tem gumbom preverjevalnik zamenja obravnavano besedo v dokumentu z besedo "
"v polju <guilabel>Zamenjaj z</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace All"
msgstr "Zamenjaj vse"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button causes the checker to replace not only the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> but to automatically make the same "
"substitution for any other occurrences of this <guilabel>Unknown word</"
"guilabel> in the document."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb povzroči, da preverjevalnik zamenja ne le trenutno <guilabel>Neznano "
"besedo:</guilabel>, temveč samodejno izvede isto zamenjavo za vse druge "
"pojavitve te <guilabel>Neznane besede</guilabel> v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore"
msgstr "Prezri"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activating this button will have the checker move on without making any "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Če aktivirate ta gumb, se bo dama premaknila naprej brez sprememb.Aktiviraje "
"tega gumba bo povzročilo, da se bo črkovalnik premaknil naprej, ne da bi "
"opravil spremembe."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1773
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore All"
msgstr "Zanemari vse"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button tells the checker to do nothing with the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> and to pass over any other instances of "
"the same word."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb sporoča preverjevalniku, naj ne naredi ničesar s trenutno "
"<guilabel>Neznano besedo:</guilabel> in prepusti vse druge primerke iste "
"besede."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This only applies to the current spellcheck run. If the checker is run again "
"later it will stop on this same word."
msgstr ""
"To velja samo za trenutno izvajanje preverjanja črkovanja. Če preverjalnik "
"pozneje znova zaženete, se bo ustavil pri tej isti besedi."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Three more buttons are located horizontally along the bottom of the "
"spellcheck dialog. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Še trije gumbi se nahajajo vodoravno na dnu pogovornega okna za preverjanje "
"črkovanja. To so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1790
#, no-c-format
msgid "This invokes the &kde; help system with the help page for this dialog."
msgstr ""
"To prikliče &kde; sistem pomoči s stranjo s pomočjo za to pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Dokončano"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1796
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button ends the spellcheck process, and returns to the document."
msgstr "Ta gumb konča postopek preverjanja črkovanja in se vrne v dokument."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button cancels the spellcheck process, all modifications are reverted, "
"and you will return to your document."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb prekliče postopek preverjanja črkovanja, vse spremembe so "
"razveljavljene in vrnili se boste v svoj dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Črkovanje (iz kazalke)...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program but it starts where your cursor is "
"instead of at the beginning of the document."
msgstr ""
"To zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja, vendar se začne tam, kjer je vaš "
"kazalec, namesto na začetku dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izbira preverjanja črkovanja ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecks the current selection."
msgstr "Preveri črkovanje trenutnega izbora."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spremeni slovar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a drop down box with all available dictionaries for spellchecking "
"at the bottom of the editor window. This allows easy switching of the "
"spellcheck dictionary &eg; for automatic spellcheck of text in different "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže spustno polje z vsemi razpoložljivimi slovarji za preverjanje "
"črkovanja na dnu okna urejevalnika. To omogoča preprosto preklapljanje med "
"slovarjem za preverjanje črkovanja &eg; za samodejno preverjanje črkovanja "
"besedila v različnih jezikih."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1852
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1856
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Editor Color Theme</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Barvna tema urejevalnika</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lists the available color schemes. You can change the schema for "
"the current view here, to change the default schema you need to use the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors\">Fonts "
"&amp; Colors</ulink> page of the config dialog."
msgstr ""
"V tem meniju so navedene razpoložljive barvne sheme. Tukaj lahko spremenite "
"shemo za trenutni pogled, če želite spremeniti privzeto shemo, morate "
"uporabiti <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors"
"\">Pisave &amp; Barve</ulink> stran konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&katepart; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&katepart; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z nastavitvami</"
"ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">meni "
"Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

