#~ "regular character keystrokes (words or expressions) would be considered "
#~ "one step and therefore be removed by a single undo operation. If the "
#~ "series of character entries were interrupted by a non-character entry "
#~ "operation (such as a backspace), invoking undo would only remove the "
#~ "entries made since that operation. The next undo would then reverse that "
#~ "operation and so on."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Skupine podobnih dejanj se v &kwrite; upoštevajo kot en sam korak <link "
#~ "linkend=\"undo\">Razveljavi</link>. Z drugimi besedami, serija "
#~ "pritisnjenih običajnih znakov se smatra za en sam korak in je odstranjena "
#~ "z eno operacijo razveljavljenja. Če je bila serija znakov prekinjena z "
#~ "vnosom, ki ni bil znak (ne primer z 'backspace') bo vpoklic razveljavitve "
#~ "odstranil le vnose narejene po tem dogodku. Naslednja razveljavitev bi "
#~ "odstranila tooperacijo in tako dalje."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When this option is not selected &kwrite; considers each keystroke to be "
